While researching cybercrime, I was surprised to learn how easily people can fall victim to phishing attacks due to lack of awareness. Even a simple email or message can trick users into sharing sensitive information. I realized that attackers often create very realistic websites and messages that are difficult to identify as fake.

As a result, I will be more cautious while using the internet and avoid clicking on unknown links. I will also make it a habit to verify the authenticity of websites and never share personal or financial information online without proper verification. This awareness will help me stay safe in the digital world.
